Program: Outlook
Title: Outlook Weekend: Long Ride to Freedom
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cstzb3
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 21 Aug 2017
Hank Thomas was on the first Freedom Ride in 1961, he was later joined by hundreds of other riders, black and white including Lewis Zuchman, Catherine Burks-Brooks, Claire O'Connor and Joan Mulholland. These are some of their stories from the long ride to freedom. Image: Freedom Bus, Jackson MS 1961 Credit: William Lovelace/Express/Getty Images Show less